{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899550/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__5_.gif?t=1725903291\" /><br><br><br><br><i>Knights of the Deep</i> is an action-packed, online fighting game with crustaceans. Battle against your friends in free for all or challenge other players in a team-based match using a variety of items and special abilities. Master each crustacean's unique fighting style and climb the hierarchy!<br><br>       <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899550/extras/Frame_1__21_.png?t=1725903291\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899550/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__7_.gif?t=1725903291\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>20 UNIQUE CHARACTERS</strong></h2><br>Each crustacean has a unique playstyle, master them all and dominate the battlefield!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899550/extras/ezgif.com-video-to-gif__2_.gif?t=1725903291\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>DEEP COMBAT SYSTEM</strong></h2><br>Claw, jump, slice, and parry your way through your rivals using a variety of special moves, split-second dodges and well-timed counter attacks.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899550/extras/ezgif.com-video-to-gif.gif?t=1725903291\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ITEMS &amp; POWER-UPS</strong></h2><br>There are items and power-ups spread all over the map, learn how to use them at the right time and change the tide of battle! Fight with guns, swords, hammers, bombs and magical staffs... or just play the mighty Fanfare!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899550/extras/ezgif.com-video-to-gif__3_.gif?t=1725903291\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>4-PLAYER SPLIT SCREEN</strong></h2>You can also play with your friends in a 4-player split screen mode. It works perfectly for couch playing, try it out!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899550/extras/serotonin_final_2.png?t=1725903291\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SEROTONIN SYSTEM</strong></h2><br>A happy crustacean hits harder than a ton of bricks. Just like in real life, a crustacean becomes more powerful as he is filled with serotonin. When his meter is full, he transforms into a dangerous wrecking-ball version of himself. Pretty simple.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SO WHAT ARE YOU WAITING FOR?</strong></h2><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899550/extras/JoinTheFight_Banner_8.png?t=1725903291\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899550/extras/banner_big_9.png?t=1725903291\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899550/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1725903291","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899550/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1725903291","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899550/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1725903291","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1899550/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1725903291","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"app